                <h1>Infographic: The Secret to Amazon's Success</h1>
            
            <div class="article-byline">
		    <ul>
            <li><div class="article-author"><a href='/author-bio/damon-poeter'><img border="0" alt="Damon Poeter" width="30" height="30" src="http://www4.pcmag.com/media/images/306956-damon-poeter.jpg?thumb=y" /></a>
			    <strong class='author'>By <span class='reviewer vcard'><a class='url fn' href='/author-bio/damon-poeter'>Damon Poeter</a></span></strong></div></li>
            <li class="date">November 18, 2011 06:29pm EST</li>
		       				          
				                <li class="commenting"><a id="top-comment-count" data-disqus-identifier="290789" href="#disqus_thread">Comments</a></li>
			                    
                <li class="email">
                   <a class="email-to-a-friend"></a> 
                   <a class="print" href="http://www.pcmag.com/article/print/290789"></a>    
                </li>
                 </ul></div>
			<div id="article-btns">
               


